node.text: Truly the sweetest guys & best dads. So thankful for my own dad and how he’s loved and supported me and cared for me so deeply. Then for John Luke and the incredible dad he is to our two little ones- so fun and helpful and steady. Just the best. And also my father-in-law who is so dependable and cooks the best food. Really grateful for these fathers who love Jesus and love our family and I count it one of the greatest blessings.

node.text: Little cousin besties!!! Life has gotten even sweeter adding Honey to the mix. So excited for these girls getting to grow up with each other🥰

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Mary Kate Robertson on May 10, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, baby, people standing, tree and outdoors.

node.text: A month with Ella and my first Mother’s Day with 2 precious little ones. Super thankful for the gift of motherhood & all that God has taught me through it and how He continues to show me Himself and His heart in it.🕊

node.text: I think I’ll always remember these days with him by those boots and the endless amount of time he wants to spend outdoors. And probably too his infinite love of ducks, dogs, and horses.🦆
